"{\"uid\": \"myrepublica.nagariknetwork.com-news-seven-sports-to-challenge-cut-from-uk-s-olympic-funding\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Subscribe Now  Seven sports, including badminton, are looking to challenge UK Sport's decision to stop funding their programs for the 2020 Olympics in Tokyo.Despite Chris Langridge and Marcus Ellis winning the men's doubles bronze in last year's Olympics, badminton had its funding cut and is among five sports which were funded for Rio 2016 and are ready to challenge the decision.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 382, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 75, \"end\": 83, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Sport\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"UK Sport\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Sport\"}, {\"begin\": 165, \"end\": 180, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chris_Langridge\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Chris Langridge\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chris_Langridge\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chris_Langridge\"}, {\"begin\": 185, \"end\": 191, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marcus_Aurelius\", \"score\": 0.9999942104697558, \"rank\": 5.789562460976109e-06, \"text\": \"Marcus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marcus_Aurelius\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marcus_Aurelius\"}, {\"begin\": 192, \"end\": 197, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Havelock_Ellis\", \"score\": 0.9708328654928954, \"rank\": 0.029383588747997375, \"text\": \"Ellis\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Havelock_Ellis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Havelock_Ellis\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We have got a really strong case.\", \"from\": 384, \"to\": 418, \"entities\": []}, {